N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 6057.7 - Liability

State Regulations

Nothing contained in this Part shall impose liability upon
the division or the State for any damages related to a registered sex
offender's access to services provided by an authorized internet entity or
damages related to any person's denial of service by an authorized internet
entity. Notes
